Package ru.nsu.shebanov.githubDomainSpecificLanguage.antlr

Class CourseDSLBaseListener

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.shebanov.githubDomainSpecificLanguage.antlr.CourseDSLBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, CourseDSLListener
public class CourseDSLBaseListener extends Object implements CourseDSLListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CourseDSLListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
